511
00:41:36,290 --> 00:41:40,589
It's a scene where you're about to perform in front of many people.

512
00:41:40,589 --> 00:41:42,350
They are screaming and cheering for you.

513
00:41:42,350 --> 00:41:44,810
You are so great.

514
00:41:44,830 --> 00:41:46,710
Just try.

515
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:51,060
Tine! You okay? Keep fighting!

516
00:41:53,380 --> 00:42:05,600
♪ I am never scared or intimidated by what is coming at me ♪

517
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:11,386
♪ I am ready to accept everything ♪

518
00:42:16,270 --> 00:42:18,080
Sarawat.

519
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:31,640
♪ As long as I have you ♪

520
00:42:31,640 --> 00:42:35,572
♪ You are all I ask for ♪

521
00:42:35,573 --> 00:42:38,779
♪ Just you ♪

522
00:42:38,780 --> 00:42:44,999
♪ I need nothing more, I want… ♪

523
00:42:44,999 --> 00:42:48,600
♪ I want to be Tine's boyfriend ♪

524
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:52,429
♪ Can I be Tine's boyfriend? ♪

525
00:42:52,429 --> 00:42:54,870
♪ Please, Tine ♪

526
00:42:54,870 --> 00:43:00,072
♪ I need nothing more ♪

527
00:43:00,072 --> 00:43:02,780
Tine, just say yes and be his boyfriend.

528
00:43:02,780 --> 00:43:05,160
My friend here is too chicken to ask you himself.

529
00:43:05,160 --> 00:43:07,460
That's why I'm doing it for him.

530
00:43:09,380 --> 00:43:11,170
Just ask him already.

531
00:43:11,170 --> 00:43:14,993
If you don't, I will freaking hit on him myself.

532
00:43:21,410 --> 00:43:22,943
Tine.

533
00:43:26,420 --> 00:43:28,440
I am so done flirting.

534
00:43:29,880 --> 00:43:31,630
Will you be my boyfriend?

